lead_paragraph: Some San Francisco Bay Area residents hoping to rent their homes for thousands of dollars a night to deep-pocketed Super Bowl attendees are finding themselves short of the goal line.

headline.print_headline: Super Bowl Home Rental Prices Not Meeting Stratospheric Hopes
